Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.62,HSubs,,0,0,0,,Kirari-sama, người chuẩn bị xong chưa ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:07.86,HSubs,,0,0,0,,Rồi, đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:16.86,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The heads of all the families are already here.}Những người đứng đầu gia tộc đã có mặt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:20.60,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Well then...} Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.94,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Shall we begin?}Bắt đầu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.74,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{How about we make it a "public match"?}Một trận đấu công khai nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.54,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{H-Hold on!}K-Khoan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:20.52,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko-senpai, weren't you gonna use your right \Nto a "public match" to challenge the student council president!?}Không phải chị bảo là dùng quyền thách \Nđấu đó cho chủ tịch Hội học sinh sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:24.58,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Oh? Did I ever say anything like that?}Ủa? Chị có nói à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.32,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She didn't!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:31.02,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What about my plan to make Yumeko president?}Thế còn kế hoạch đưa Yumeko lên chủ tịch của mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:35.38,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'm afraid I'm just not that patient.}Chị không thể chờ được nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.40,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{So, Manyuda-san, shall we play?}Nào, chúng ta chơi chứ Mayunda?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.12,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{See? I told you.}Nói rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:49.86,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{When everything seems to be going great,\Nthat's often a sign that it's all falling apart behind the scenes.}Khi mọi chuyện diễn ra suôn sẻ thì chắc chắn sẽ bị phá.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:51.98,HSubs,,0,0,0,,Sao nào Mayunda?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:56.56,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I get it now.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:59.58,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{My calculations were wrong.}Tính toán của mình đã sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:02.00,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{After all that, I still underestimated that girl.}Vì đã coi thường cô ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:05.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{This girl is gambling just for the sake of gambling.}Cô ta chơi bạc chỉ để thỏa mãn sở thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.36,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Jabami Yumeko is a gambling addict.}Jabami Yumeko là con nghiện cờ bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:13.70,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The result is not what she's after.\NShe's just a slave to gambling.}Cô ta không quan tâm đến kết quả. \NChỉ đơn thuần là một nô lệ cờ bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.80,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{This makes it even easier.}Thế càng đơn giản.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.28,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'll just add it to my calculations.}Mình chỉ cần thay đổi tính toán.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Alright. I accept your "public match".}Được. Tôi chấp nhận trận đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.06,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Why did it end up like this...?}Tại sao chuyện này...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:32.06,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Two council members losing to her in front of everyone here...}Hai thành viên hội học sinh thua trước mọi người...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.00,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{We absolutely cannot allow it.}Không thể để chuyện đó xảy ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:40.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{And on top of that,\NManyuda is probably the one behind all this Yumemite plot.}Và có vẻ Mayunda là kẻ đứng sau vụ của Yumemite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:45.02,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If he wins, the traitor is going to get even more powerful.}Nếu anh ta thắng, thế lực thù địch với Hội trưởng sẽ mạnh hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:51.46,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Our president spent so much time building the student council,\Nand now it's falling apart because I'm powerless to stop it.}Hội trưởng đã cố gắng xây dựng mọi thứ, \Nvà giờ nó bị phá hủy chỉ vì mình quá yếu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:57.44,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko-chan, what about the rules and the game?\NWe better find a dealer soon if you need one.}Yumeko này, định chơi trò gì? Có lẽ ta nên tìm người làm cái trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.32,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I will be your dealer.}Để tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.12,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The vice president?}Phó chủ tịch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:09.30,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Fine with me.\NWhat game do we play?}Vậy cũng được. Thế chơi trò gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:15.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Since all of this is sudden,\Nwe will play an original game using standard playing cards.}Do trận này khá bất ngờ nên ta sẽ sử dụng bài thông thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.86,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The name is "Choice Poker".}Tên của trò này là "Choice Poker".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.46,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The basic rules are the same as regular poker.}Luật cơ bản cũng như Poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:26.60,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Each of you will be dealt five cards and\None chance to exchange them.}Mỗi người sẽ được 5 lá và một cơ hội thay đổi bài.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:30.88,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{We will use a Joker so the deck will have 53 cards.}Chúng ta cũng sẽ dùng thêm 1 lá Joker .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:34.70,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{But unlike the regular poker,\Nyou can't "fold" or "call" in this game.}Nhưng luật chơi trò này sẽ không có Fold (bỏ bài) và Call (theo cược).
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.30,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You can only make a bet or raise the previous one.}Chỉ có thể Bet (cược) hoặc Raise (tăng cược).
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:46.20,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You will show your cards at each hand.\NAnd whoever's bet more in the end will get the right to make a choice.}Bạn sẽ mở bài trên tay. Và ai cược cuối cùng sẽ có một lựa chọn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.46,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{A "choice"?\NWhat kind of choice?}Lựa chọn? Chọn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:55.14,HSubs,,0,0,0,,"Stronger" hoặc "Weaker".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:05:00.90,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{In regular poker, the strongest hand always wins.}Trong trò Poker bình thường, bài mạnh hơn dĩ nhiên sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:08.92,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{But in this game, if you got the right to "choose",\Nyou can decide which hand wins - the stronger one, or the weaker one.}Nhưng trong trò này, nếu "lựa chọn" đúng, \Nta có thể quyết định ai thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:15.04,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If you go for stronger, then it's like a regular poker.\NThe strongest hand wins.}Nếu chọn Stronger thì kẻ mạnh hơn sẽ \Nthắng giống như Poker thông thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:22.82,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{But If you go for weaker, then hand strength is reversed.\NWhoever has the weaker hand wins.}Nhưng nếu chọn Weaker thì bài ai yếu hơn sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:27.22,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If you have the chips then you can win even with the bad hand.}Thế nên dù bài xấu nhưng lựa chọn đúng vẫn thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.06,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{A fitting game for our academy, don't you think?}Một trò chơi quá hợp với học viện này, phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Those are the rules.}Luật chỉ có thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.78,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You may bet as much as you want.\NLet's see how long you can last.}Hãy cược hết tất cả mọi thứ mình có đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:40.88,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I see. Even if your hand is weak,\Nyou can still win if you have money to bet.}Ra là thế. Dù bài yếu nhưng nếu đủ tiền \Nđể tăng cược thì vẫn thắng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.58,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Rules are simple.}Luật chơi quá đơn giản.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:46.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Except for that "choice" thing, it all seems pretty basic.}Trừ cái vụ "Lựa chọn" ra thì có vẻ bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.06,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What the hell are those rules...?}Luật kiểu quái gì vậy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:51.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{This is bad. It's just so obvious...}Nguy quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.14,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean?}Ý cậu là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:58.22,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You don't get it? No matter how you think about those rules,\NYumeko is at a disadvantage.}Không hiểu à? Luật như thế rõ ràng làm Yumeko bất lợi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.10,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Chances of her winning are practically zero.}Cơ hội để cậu ấy thắng thực tế là 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Any objections?}Có phản đối gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.00,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.08,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Fine with me.}Tôi cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:09.40,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Then let's start "Choice Poker".}Vậy thì bắt đầu nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:13.68,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{"Disadvantage"? What do you mean?}"Bất lợi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:18.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{In regular poker, having more money to bet gives you an advantage.\NYou know that, right?}Trong Poker bình thường, càng tăng cược nhiều\N thì khả năng thắng càng cao, phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.90,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You can pressure your opponents by raising the bet.}Ta có thể gây áp lực cho đối thủ nhờ tăng tiền cược.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:29.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Even if you have a bad hand,\Nyou can still win if you can make them fold.}Dù bài có xấu nhưng chỉ cần tăng cược \Nlàm đối phương bỏ cuộc là thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:33.56,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's why bluffing is vital in poker.}Thế nên Poker chủ yếu là mánh khóe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:39.78,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{But in this game you can continue to play\Nas long as you have at least one chip.}Nhưng trong trò này ta có thể chơi tiếp miễn sao còn 1 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Though it means you won't get the "choice".}Thế nên vẫn có cơ hội chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{And that will be the end of her.}Nhưng nếu không "lựa chọn" được sẽ là kết thúc cho chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:47.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{A player with the "choice" can always give his hand an advantage.}Ai nắm quyền "lựa chọn" sẽ có lợi thế lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:56.40,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{In other words...\NIt's a poker where one side }{\i1}{always}{\i0}{ has a winning hand.}Hay nói cách khác...kẻ đó có thể quyết định trận đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:07:02.56,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Unless I was sure that I had more money to bet, \NI'd never accept this game.}Phải có rất nhiều tiền mới dám chơi trò này.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.66,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Even an idiot could see that.}Ngu lắm cũng phải hiểu chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:08.78,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{B-But, Yumeko has lots of cash, I think?}N-Nhưng Yumeko có nhiều tiền mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.94,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You better be careful around the student council.}Đừng xem thường lũ Hội học sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.52,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{One chip will be worth 10 million yen.}1 xèng là 10 triệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.28,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{How many do you want?}Cô muốn bao nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:25.32,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I have earned 310 million in cash so I'll take 31 chips, please.}Tôi vừa kiếm được 310 triệu nên sẽ lấy 31 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:26.94,HSubs,,0,0,0,,Manyuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.64,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Well, for now...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.16,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'll take 100 chips.}Tôi lấy 100 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:33.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What!?}Cái gì?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.46,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{A hundred?}100?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.64,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's a billion yen!}Là 1 tỷ yên à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.64,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's crazy!}Điên à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:39.30,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Not surprising. He's got a ton of financial backup.}Quả nhiên có hậu thuẫn khủng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:43.16,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{And knowing Manyuda-senpai, he's got a lot more.}Có lẽ anh ấy còn nhiều hơn số đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:44.90,HSubs,,0,0,0,,Yumeko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.60,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{First, ante up.}Đầu tiên là phí tham gia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.78,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{One chip each.}Mỗi người 1 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:55.60,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Oh, that reminds me.}A, nhắc mới nhớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:08:01.54,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Since I've never gone for "weakest" before,\Nwho wins if none of us has anything?}Nếu như hai người đều không có gì thì sao? (hòa)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:06.60,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If neither of you has anything,\Nthe highest card is the strongest.}Ta xét bộ nào mạnh hơn sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:13.92,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{For example, a King in one hand is stronger\Nthan a Ten in the other hand.}Ví dụ Già Bích sẽ mạnh hơn 10 cơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.98,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I see. Thank you!}Vậy à? Cám ơn nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:21.22,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Acting like you're going for the weakest, huh.\NVery clever.}Giả bộ ngu ngốc à? Khá đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:24.36,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'll change two cards.}Thế thì tớ sẽ đổi 2 lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:26.06,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{One for me.}Tôi 1 lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:30.60,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Alright, now place your bets.}Rồi, hãy đặt cược.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.98,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Jabami discarded a King and a Jack.}Jabami bỏ Già cơ và Bồi rô.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:40.16,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If she's going for a "weak" hand then\Nit's natural to throw away strong cards.}Nếu cô ta chọn "Weaker" thì vứt bỏ những lá này là hiển nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.82,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{However...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:47.10,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's possible that her other three cards might be a three of a kind.}Có khả năng 3 lá còn lại sẽ cùng bộ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:51.46,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{And even if they're not, she still might have an Ace.}Và nếu không phải thì cô ta hẳn phải có Xì.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:57.78,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She's doing the a "weaker" hand on purpose in order\Nto make me choose "stronger".}Cô ta cố tình làm thế để lừa mình chọn "Stronger".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:01.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I tried to get a straight and failed so I got nothing.}Lúc đó mình sẽ cố kiếm sảnh và thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:04.80,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Is Jabami going for "stronger" or "weaker"...?}Vậy Jabami sẽ nhắm vào "Weaker" hay "Stronger"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:08.74,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I need some data to work with.\NI'll test you!}Mình cần thêm thông tin. Phải nhử cô ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.62,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I bet ten chips.}Cược 10 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.32,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Ten? A hundred million just like that?}10? 100 triệu yên sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Jabami, are you going to raise?}Jabami, có tăng cược không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.54,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'll raise ten chips.\NSo it's twenty-one in total.}Tăng thêm 10 xèng. Tổng cộng là 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:28.46,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko only has thirty-one chips.\NIf she loses that, over half of her bank will be gone.}Yumeko chỉ có 31 xèng. Nếu thua sẽ mất gần nửa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:30.62,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Manyuda, raising?}Mayunda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:31.80,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{No need.}Không cần.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:35.16,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Jabami's bet was the last one so now she has the "choice".}Jabami cược cuối nên sẽ được "lựa chọn".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:38.06,HSubs,,0,0,0,,"Stronger" hay "weaker"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.20,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Let's see...}Xem nào...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.86,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{How about "stronger"?}Stronger nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.40,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{"Stronger".\NIn that case...}"Stronger"...Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.00,HSubs,,0,0,0,,Showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:50.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Got nothing.}Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.22,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Nothing here.}Cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:56.02,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Both of you have nothing.\NBut Jabami has an Ace high so she wins this round.}Cả hai đều không có gì nhưng Jabami có Xì cao hơn sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:59.42,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes! That gives her some money to spare.}May quá! Có thêm ít tiền rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Now, let's start the next round.}Giờ thì, vòng tiếp theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:11.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hmm, what should I do?\NIt's hard to get used to these rules.}Làm sao giờ? Luật này khó chơi quá à...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.68,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I get it, alright.}Tôi biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:18.32,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Unlike normal poker, big raises are meaningless here.}Khác với Poker bình thường, cược lớn chẳng có ý nghĩa gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:23.68,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{As long as you bet one chip more than your opponent,\Nyou will have the "choice".}Chỉ cần cược hơn đối thủ 1 xèng là có quyền "lựa chọn".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:29.38,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{This game is all about raising again and again by one chip.}Thế nên bản chất trò này tăng cược từng xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:38.34,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's only worth it if you want to pressure your opponent.\NBut even then it takes only one chip to ruin this strategy.}Nó có thể gây áp lực cho đối phương \Nnhưng cũng phá hủy chiến thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:42.76,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{A risk without much in the terms of reward.}Rất nhiều rủi ro xảy ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:46.94,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{But Jabami Yumeko did that anyway.}Nhưng Jabami Yumeko chắc chắn sẽ làm thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:52.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Because she's insane.\NThis girl gets off on taking such risks.}Vì cô ta rất thích sự rủi ro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:58.98,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If I wasn't aware of that already,\Nthat illogical raise might've thrown me off.}Nếu không nhận thức được điều đó, \Ncô ta sẽ làm mình hoảng loạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Now I can add her eccentric behavior into my calculations.}Giờ thì mình sẽ thêm cách chơi lập dị của cô ta vào tính toán.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:07.86,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You have my gratitude,\NNishinotouin, Ikishima, Yumemite...}Cám ơn nhé Nishinotouin, Ikishima, Yumemite...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:15.10,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Thanks for serving as footholds for me.}vì đã phục vụ tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The situation is...}Tình hình...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.76,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko has forty-two.}Yumeko đang có 42 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.58,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Manyuda got eighty-nine.}Mayunda có 89 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.02,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's enough to go on the offensive.}Nếu phòng thủ sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.04,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko can win this.}Yumeko có thể thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:31.52,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{No matter the odds, she's always won in the past.}Cho đến giờ, cậu ấy vẫn luôn thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.54,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{And this time it's the same.}Và lần này cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:37.04,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She'll win using some method that I can't even think of.}Cậu ấy sẽ thắng bằng cách mà mình không thể đoán.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.36,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Changing cards?}Có đổi bài không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:40.52,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Hmm, let's see...}Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.80,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'll change two.}Đổi hai lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:47.48,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She's gonna change a pair of Tens?}Đổi cặp 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:48.58,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What the heck?}Cái quái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.26,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Why would anyone do that?}Tại sao lại làm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.48,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I don't get it.}Chả hiểu gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.28,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I can think of two reasons.}Chỉ có hai lý do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:56.06,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{One - she's going for a bad hand.}1 - cô ta nhắm đến bài xấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:12:03.42,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{But I'm going to get the "choice" here.\NIt'd be a suicide to reveal that she goes for a weaker hand.}Nhưng trận này sẽ là mình "lựa chọn". \NCô ta tự đâm đầu vào chỗ chết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:08.36,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Two - she was dealt a two pair or a full house.}2 - cô ta có 2 cặp hoặc 3 lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:16.98,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She wants me to think that she's going for a weaker hand,\Nmake me choose "stronger" and then win with a pair or three of a kind.}Như vậy sẽ lừa mình chọn "Stronger" và sau đó thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:21.74,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{However there's only a 4.76% of getting two pair in the first deal.}Tuy nhiên, xác suất có 2 đôi ngay lượt đầu chỉ là 4.76%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:25.20,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{And for a full house, it's only 0.14%.}Và cù lủ là 0.14%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:29.34,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Even if she had that good of a hand,\Nwould she just throw it away like that?}Nhưng bài đẹp như thế mà cô ta vẫn bỏ đi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:36.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She'd have a better chance if she kept quiet and\Nhoped that I choose "stronger".}Như thế thà im lặng và chờ mình chọn "Stronger" thì hay hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:45.42,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{In other words, the chances of getting those cards\Nand pointlessness of trying to bluff is ridiculous no matter how you look at it.}Nói cách khác, không thể nào xảy ra hai trường hợp trên cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.28,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's assuming she is a normal opponent.}Đó là đối với người bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:54.48,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The fact that I'm gambling with Jabami Yumeko is ridiculous in itself.}Còn đối thủ của mình là Jabami Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:13:00.14,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I already know she won against student council members in unusual ways.}Mình đã hiểu cách cô ta đánh bại các thành viên Hội học sinh rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.20,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{This girl plays in a way that makes—}Cách chơi của cô ta lúc này...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Manyuda, your move?}Mayunda, sao nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.36,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{...no sense!}...là vô nghĩa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.64,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Changing five cards?}Đổi hết 5 lá?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:09.78,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:12.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I am changing nothing.}Không đổi lá nào cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:14.56,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{W-What is he...?}V-Vậy là sao...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.66,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{He's taunting Yumeko into betting.}Hắn đang dụ Yumeko cược.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:20.04,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If Yumeko gets the right to choose now, she wins.}Nếu Yumeko "lựa chọn" đúng, cậu ấy sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:23.48,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{But the only way to do that is to bet big.}Và cách duy nhất để "lựa chọn" là tăng cược.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:28.78,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If Yumeko-senpai doesn't like her hand,\Nshe doesn't have to go that far.}Nếu Yumeko không có bài tốt thì sẽ không theo được.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:31.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She only has to play when her hand is good enough.}Chị ấy chỉ có thể đấu khi bài đủ tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:34.52,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What is Manyuda-senpai even doing?}Vậy mục đích của anh Mayunda là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:38.28,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That move is nothing but risk. It's stupid.}Bước đi này quá rủi ro. Anh ta bị điên à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:46.46,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's good. Sending me a challenge like that?}Hay đấy. Thách thức tớ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:51.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Well, if that's what's on your mind,\NI'm not about to lose!}Thế thì tớ cũng không chịu thua đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.00,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'll bet.\NForty-one chips!}Tăng cược 41 xèng!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.54,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She's going all-in!? Why is she doing that!?}Chơi hết sao? Tại sao chị ta làm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:01.28,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{No mistake about it. He saw right through Yumeko.}Quả nhiên hắn ta đang nhắm đến điều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I raise. One chip.}Theo. Tăng thêm 1 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.22,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Jabami, any response?}Jabami, tăng cược chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:07.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.40,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Manyuda, your choice?}Mayunda, lựa chọn là?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:10.46,HSubs,,0,0,0,,"Stronger".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:14.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{No hesitation. I'd do the same thing as well.}Nếu là mình cũng làm thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:19.22,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko changed a pair of Tens so chances are\Nshe's got a bad hand now.}Chị ấy bỏ cặp 10 tức là khả năng bài yếu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:21.62,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{In theory, he's made the best decision.}Về lý thuyết, anh ta đã chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:25.02,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{No. I have to believe in Jabami Yumeko's abilities!}Không, phải tin tưởng chị ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.50,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If Yumeko loses now then it's all over for me.}Nếu Yumeko thua, cuộc đời mình cũng bế mạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.02,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She's got to win this!}Phải thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:32.14,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You've made your choice.\NSo now...}Đã chọn. Vậy kết quả là...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.60,HSubs,,0,0,0,,Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:37.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,...down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.32,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I got nothing!}Tớ không có gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.10,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Unfortunately.}Thật xui xẻo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.26,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She lo—}Chị ấy thu--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:47.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yumeko-chan lost.}Yumeko-chan thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.56,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Seriously?}Đùa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.44,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{She had nothing?}Hết sạch xèng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:52.70,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What the hell are you doing, Jabami Yumeko!?}Chị làm trò gì vậy, Jabami Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:59.50,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Your winning was my only chance to get back on the council...}Chiến thắng của chị là cơ hội duy nhất cho em...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.32,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'm finished...}Kết thúc rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:03.28,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's all over for me...}Đời mình bế mạc...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:06.86,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I see. She was going for a straight, huh.}Ra là thế. Nhắm đến sảnh à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:11.26,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That would never happen.\NAn odd choice.}Lựa chọn vớ vẩn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:16.54,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Well, all these moves she makes are part of my calculations.}Nhưng cô ta y như mình tính toán.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:21.28,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If you think of Jabami Yumeko as a normal opponent,\Nyou're going to lose.}Nếu nghĩ Jabami Yumeko là một đổi thủ bình thường, mình sẽ thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:29.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{"She's betting 410 million, she must be up to something".\NThat's what she tries to make you think.}"Cô ta cược hết 410 triệu. Chắc chắn đang định làm gì đó". \NĐó là cách cô ta lừa mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.36,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{But I am different.}Nhưng tôi thì khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:33.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I just have to stick to the core fundamentals.}Chỉ cần dựa vào giá trị cốt lõi là đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:38.76,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{With my starting bankroll, I always had the advantage in this game.}Với khả năng tài chính thì ngay từ đầu mình đã chiến thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:43.76,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If I didn't let her faze me and stuck to a sensible strategy,\NI couldn't lose.}Chừng nào còn tỉnh táo trước cô ta thì mình sẽ không thể thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:50.62,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Jabami Yumeko. You're just another paving stone on the road to my victory.}Jabami Yumeko, cô chỉ là một viên đá lót đường cho tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.38,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{This game is over.}Game over nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{And you're over too.}Và cả cô nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:59.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Jabami, you're out of chips.\NDo you want to continue playing?}Jabami, cô đã hết xèng. Có muốn cược tiếp không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:00.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Sumeragi-san, will that be alright?}Sumeragi ới ơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.20,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{M-Me?}E-Em?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:13.04,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{How much can you give me?}Em đưa cho chị được bao nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.40,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Wha?}Cái--?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Sumeragi-san, how about it?}Sumeragi, sao nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.34,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{T-That...}C-Chuyện này...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:24.88,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The other day you said you wanted to be my friend, right?}Tuần trước em bảo muốn làm bạn chị mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:28.34,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I think you said you wanted me \Nto become student council president?}Em còn bảo muốn chị làm Hội trưởng cơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.88,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{When friend's in trouble,\Nwe have to help each other out, right?}Khi bạn bè gặp khó khăn phải giúp đỡ nhau chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:38.26,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I've used up all my cash so now I'm trouble.\NWould you mind helping me out?}Chị hết sạch tiền và đang khó khăn lắm, cho mượn ít nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:44.86,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Sumeragi. You got kicked from the council,\Nso now you're stuck to Jabami Yumeko?}Sumeragi, bị đá khỏi Hội học sinh và giờ bám váy Yumeko à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:49.02,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Give it up.\NI'll let it slide this if you do.}Bỏ đi. Tôi sẽ tha thứ cho em.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.64,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Or do you intend to go against the council?}Hay muốn chống hội học sinh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:56.06,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I guess I should expect nothing less from you.}Mà anh còn lạ gì em.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:17:00.50,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{My recommendation got you in the student council after all.}Dù sao thì anh đã khuyên em vào Hội học sinh mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:04.58,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Your ambition.\NYour will to do whatever it takes to get to the top.}Em rất tham vọng. Sẽ làm mọi thứ để lên đỉnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:06.56,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I saw all of that in you.}Anh biết hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:12.52,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Ambition lies at the heart of self-growth and struggle.\NIt's essential for any leader.}Tham vọng sẽ mang lại đấu tranh và phát triển. \NLà một tố chất cần có của lãnh đạo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:16.22,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{And that's one thing we have in common.}Và anh với em có điểm chung đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:20.66,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{To be honest, I even felt a sort of affinity for you.}Nói thật, anh thấy thích thú với em đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.42,HSubs,,0,0,0,,Manyuda-senpai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:23.66,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{However...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:28.14,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You don't have the talent to make your ambitions come true.}Em không có khả năng để biến tham vọng của mình thành hiện thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:31.44,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You're out of your league.\NThat's all there is to it.}Tóm lại là con vô dụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:33.94,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Talent is about getting results.}Tài năng liên quan đến thành quả.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:37.38,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{A loser like you won't have anything like that.}Kẻ thua cuộc như em không có thứ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.90,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Give it up.}Bỏ cuộc đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You don't have what it takes to take the high road here.}Người như em không có tư cách đứng ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:43.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Ah, yes.}A phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:47.98,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If you want to get your council seat back,\NI can arrange that.}Nếu muốn vào lại Hội học sinh, anh sẽ sắp xếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:52.88,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You can prove yourself useful,\Nas long as you realize your strengths.}Em có thể chứng minh mình vẫn hữu dụng. \NĐến khi nào tìm ra được sức mạnh bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:55.62,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{So come back, Sumeragi.}Quay lại đi, Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.44,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I-I...}E-Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:58.54,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{My, my.}Chà chà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That's rather harsh.}Nói lời cay đắng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:04.16,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Sumeragi-san has no talent?}Sumeragi không có tài năng?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.08,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Who exactly decided that for her?}Ai quyết định điều đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:12.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{And even if that's true,\Nwhy is that a reason to throw away her ambitions like that?}Và ngay cả khi không có thì ai cấm em ấy từ bỏ tham vọng?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.90,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Because it's for her own sake.}Cũng vì lợi ích của em ấy thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:21.46,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{No matter how much talentless try,\Nthey only make things worse.}Những kẻ bất tài dù có cố gắng cũng chỉ làm mọi chuyện tệ hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:25.54,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That effort is worthless, so it's better to give up.}Nỗ lực vô ích thì nên bỏ cuộc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.04,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I don't know about that.}Chưa chắc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.78,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The only one who can decide her worth is Sumeragi-san herself.}Người duy nhất được quyết định chính là bản thân Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:38.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Sumeragi-san. If you want earn something,\Nyou need to reach out for it first.}Sumeragi, nếu muốn thứ gì đó thì phải tìm nó trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:45.50,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Professional athletes give up their teenage years to train.\NBusiness owners put up collateral to borrow money.}Vận động viên bỏ học để luyện tập.\N Doanh nhân vay ngân hàng đầu tư.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:49.98,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{To make your ambitions come true,\Nyou have to take risks.}Muốn biến tham vọng thành sự thật thì phải chịu rủi ro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.20,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The bigger your ambition, the greater the risk.}Tham vọng càng lớn thì rủi ro càng cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:58.62,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That might take time or enough work to shorten your lifespan.}Nó có thể tốn thời gian và công sức cả đời.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{This time it only comes down money.}Lần này chỉ là vấn đề tiền bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.56,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Now...!}Nào...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.92,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Make your choice, please!}Hãy lựa chọn đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.06,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Leave in peace as an incompetent person...}Sống trong yên bình...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{...or risk losing it all to get to the very top.}...hay đánh cược với rủi ro để đứng trên đỉnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.40,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The one who needs to decide is you!}Em là người quyết định đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.32,HSubs,,0,0,0,,Sumeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:17.40,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What do I do?}Mình phải làm sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:23.44,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If I stick with Manyuda-senpai, then I can get back on the council\Nand inherit the family business again.}Nếu theo anh Mayunda, mình sẽ vào lại Hội học sinh và kế thừa tập đoàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:29.42,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Or if I stay with Yumeko, if she wins... That's one thing.\NBut if she loses, I'll be done for.}Còn nếu theo Yumeko, cô ta thắng... \Nmình có hết, cô ta thua... mình mất hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:30.74,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What do I do?}Phải làm sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.28,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{What should I do?}Làm sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.04,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You want to join the student council?}Em muốn vào Hội học sinh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.10,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Yes!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:39.70,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Did you see the last contribution rankings?}Anh đã xem bảng xếp hạng đóng góp chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.16,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{That shows how serious I am about this.}Nó chứng minh cho sự nghiêm túc của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:43.74,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Don't do it.}Dừng lại đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.74,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Wha—?\NWhy is that?}T-Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.92,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You're after the power that a council seat gives you, right?}Em muốn theo đuổi quyền lực phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:53.20,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's true, the current student council wields absolute power.}Đúng là hiện tại thì Hội học sinh quyền lực nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:57.38,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{We can exploit the student body and earn all the money and prestige we want.}Chúng ta có thể sử dụng học sinh và kiếm tiền cũng như uy tín thoải mái.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Nobody can defy us.}Không ai dám phủ nhận nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:02.40,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The student council controls everything in this academy.}Hội học sinh kiểm soát mọi thứ ở học viện này.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:08.44,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I understand that.\NYou've got hundreds of people who want to join the council.}Em hiểu. Ý anh là có hàng trăm người muốn vào vị trí này.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:10.90,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{But I have money on my side.}Nhưng em có tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:14.44,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I can make a real contribution to the council.}Em sẽ đóng góp vào Hội học sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:17.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Even more than I already did, if you need it...}Nếu cần nhiều thì em cũng có thể chuẩn bị...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.28,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I see. You just don't get it, huh?}Em vẫn không hiểu à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:22.82,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{The council rules over this academy.}Hội học sinh kiểm soát học viện này.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:28.08,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{We are responsible for everything here.}Chúng ta phải chịu mọi trách nhiệm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:35.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Our grads form the core of Japan.\NThey watch us and have high expectations.}Học sinh ở đây là cốt lõi của toàn đất nước. \NNhững người phía trên rất kỳ vọng vào chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:44.44,HSubs,,0,0,0,,Nếu ta phản bội lại họ, tất cả sẽ kết thúc.\N Vì thế không thể lơ là dù chỉ 1 giây.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.80,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{All that responsibility lies on our shoulders.}Trách nhiệm cho việc đó sẽ đổ hết lên đầu Hội học sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.48,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You think you're ready for that?}Em đã chuẩn bị tinh thần chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:53.22,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If you understand that then go home.}Nếu hiểu rồi thì về đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.78,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{You'd be much happier living a life of a normal student.}Sống yên ổn, làm một học sinh bình thường vẫn tốt hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.92,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I want to be council president.}Em muốn thành Hội trưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:01.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Excuse me?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:07.60,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{My father ordered me to join the council, but...}Mệnh lệnh của cha em là vào được Hội học sinh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.34,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I don't want to end it there.}nhưng em không muốn thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.96,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{If I have to do it, I'm want to be king!}Nếu đã làm thì phải thành vua!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.94,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'm willing to bet everything on that.}Em sẽ làm mọi thứ để đạt được nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:21.70,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Who cares about grads or people who don't like me?\NLet them come. I'll deal with all of them!}Ai quan tâm đến những kẻ đó chứ!\N Chịu trách nhiệm á? Em cân hết!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:27.36,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'll do anything to take the president's seat,\Nand you're saying it's not good enough?}Em sẽ làm mọi cách để lấy được \Ncái ghế hội trưởng! Như vậy có gì sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.88,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{We're the same. You and I.}Em giống anh đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:40.08,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{It's true. You did contribute a lot.\NAnd your resume is good.}Em đóng góp khá nhiều. Hồ sơ cũng không vấn đề.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:44.02,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{So be it.\NI'll make a recommendation.}Rồi. Anh sẽ giới thiệu em vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:46.24,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{We will become kings.}Chúng ta sẽ trở thành vua.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:49.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I hope you're ready for that, Sumeragi Itsuki!}Em hãy chuẩn bị tinh thần đi, Sumeragi Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:51.46,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Of course!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I thought I was being recognized.}Mình nghĩ đã được công nhận.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:58.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{As a friend who had the same goal and the same secret.}Bởi một người bạn cùng chung chí hướng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:02.62,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{As two partners who were after the president's seat.}Giống một đôi bạn có 1 mục tiêu chung.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.72,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I thought we both felt the same way.}Và cả hai đều có suy nghĩ giống nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:08.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{But I was wrong.}Nhưng không.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:12.30,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'm just another pawn to him.}Mình chỉ là viên đá lót đường cho hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:14.84,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{One to throw away when it's no longer useful.}Khi hết giá trị sẽ bị vứt bỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:17.40,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{This whole time he was looking down on me.}Mình đã bị hắn lợi dụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:21.18,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{So, Sumeragi-san...}Nào, Sumeragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:24.58,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{Shall we go through this together?}Hãy cùng chị cờ bạc điên cuồng nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:27.50,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I will get back at him!}Phải trả đủ cho hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:32.56,HSubs,,0,0,650,,{Episode 10: Selective Girl}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:32.62,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I want you to add 100 chips from Yumeko, please!}100 xèng cho Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:35.58,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{I'm the only one...}Tôi sẽ trở thành...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:37.54,HSubs,,0,0,0,,{...who's gonna be king!}...vua!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:39.54,HSubs,,0,0,0,,
